{
  "texts": [
    "Each dataset follows the SVC model with p = 2 predictors, using the following parameter configuration:",
    "• Fixed effects: α = (-5, 10) ⊤",
    "• Spatial range parameters: ϕ = (40, 15) ⊤ • Variance parameters: σ 2 = (15, 30) ⊤",
    "• Nugget variance: τ 2 = 0.1",
    "For each simulated dataset, we compute both the true likelihood using Genz's algorithm (Genz, 1992) for multivariate normal integrals and the proposed Vecchia approximation with conditioning set sizes M ∈ {10, 30, 50}."
  ]
}